comments.body:
Find the explicit declaration in the class/object so that we can infer the indent from them.

```scala
object X {
  trait Foo {
    def foo(x: Int): Int
  }
  class Bar extends Foo {
               val x = 1
  }
}
```

to 

```scala
object X {
  // ...
  class Bar extends Foo {
          override def foo(x: Int): Int = ???
          val x = 1
  }
}
```

instead of 

```scala
object X {
  // ...
  class Bar extends Foo {
    override def foo(x: Int): Int = ???
          val x = 1
  }
}
```

